<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA35">
<l>niṉṟu miruntuṅ kiṭantun tiritantu</l>
<l>moṉṟumō vāṟṟāṉeṉ ṉeñcakalā ṉaṉṟaṅkai</l>
<l>vaṉpuṭaiyāṟ poṉpeyarōṉ vāytakarttu mārviṭantā</l>
<l>ṉaṉpuṭaiya ṉaṉṟē yavaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing, sitting, lying and roaming about</l>
<l>he cannot cease from anyone, he does not depart from my heart,</l>
<l>he who dug the chest, breaking the mouth of the gold-coloured one</l>
<l>with the strong side of [his] palm that day, he possesse love [towards us], isn’t it?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
